Reorder column of Dataframe

Source: R/reorder.R
reorder.Rd

select data as given column's order. Column provided as character.

Usage

reorder(inputData, columns)

Arguments

inputData

data frame to reorder

columns

vector of column names

Value

data frame with column order changed

See also

dplyr's select_ function

Examples

reorder(iris, c('Species', 'Sepal.Length', 'Sepal.Width', 'Petal.Length', 'Petal.Width'))
